  ('PL-007', 'Wroclaw Technology Park – Labs & Prototype Workshops', 'Wroclawski Park Technologiczny S.A.', 'Incubator / Accelerator', 'PL', 'Wroclaw', 51.093, 16.976, ARRAY['Life Sciences & Biotech','Advanced Materials','Advanced Manufacturing']::text[], ARRAY['Wet Lab','Prototyping / Makerspace','Pilot Line / Scale-up']::text[], 'Fee-for-service', 'Biotech & chemistry labs, drug-development lab, prototyping workshops; equipment rentable per hour/day or exclusively', 'WPT offers 14 labs and prototype workshops (6,000+ m2) rentable per hour, per day or per workstation to startups and companies, with de minimis support cutting costs.', 'technologpark.pl', 'approved'),
